-- Sawiris-Beltone refuse offered 9.49 percent stake in EFG Hermes
-- 
-- Mon Jul 07, 2014 04:00AM EDT
-- None



CAIRO, July 7 (Reuters) - Egypt's Beltone Financial <BTFH.CA> and billionaire Naguib Sawiris refused to accept an offered 9.5 percent stake in EFG Hermes <HRHO.CA>, less than half the amount sought, they said in a joint statement on Monday.

